column12: Oh, it gladdens my heart to finally see you again.
Come, Kainé. Come to your Grandma's side.
You've been lonely for so, so long...
So much pain... So much despair... Why go on living anymore?
Don't speak to your Grandma like—
You're going to stop talking now.
And then I'm gonna slooowly walk over to you...
cram my hand inside your goddamn bitch-ass chest, and PULL OUT YOUR FUCKING HEART!
